               <p>1:1; </p>
                           <p>2:1; </p>
                           <p>3:1;  3:98;</p>
                           <p>5:1; </p>
                           <p>7:1; </p>
                           <p>9:1; </p>
                           <p>10:1;</p>
                           <p>11:1; </p>
                           <p>12:1; </p>
                           <p>13:1</p>
                        </note>
                        <note>The text has been translated from the Greek <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1219Bible#t6greekLXX"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT1219Bible#t6greekLXX</span></ref>.</note>
                        <note>See also <ref target="#chapter7"/>.</note>
